<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ALEF Online Academy Careers</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .banner {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: #FDE8DB;
            border: 1px solid #F48C4A;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            margin-bottom: 40px; /* Increased margin-bottom for spacing */
        }

        .banner-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .banner-text {
            max-width: 600px;
        }

            .banner-text h1 {
                font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
                font-size: 40px;
                color: #583017;
            }

            .banner-text p {
                font-size: 20px;
                color: #1A1A1A;
            }

        .banner-image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .apply-button {
            background: #3E4997;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .interns, .growth {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px; /* Increased margin-bottom for spacing */
        }

            .interns img, .growth img {
                width: 50%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 50px;
                box-shadow: 0px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            }

            .interns p, .growth p {
                width: 50%;
                font-size: 20px;
                color: #000000;
            }

        .join {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px; /* Increased margin-bottom for spacing */
        }

            .join h2 {
                font-size: 36px;
                font-weight: 600;
                text-transform: uppercase;
            }

        .call-to-action {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #F48C4A;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 20px;
        }

            .call-to-action h3 {
                font-size: 2em;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            .call-to-action p {
                font-size: 1.2em;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .call-to-action a {
                color: #424994;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-weight: bold;
                font-size: 1.2em;
            }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <main>
        <section class="banner">
            <div class="banner-content">
                <div class="banner-text">
                    <h1>Join ALEF Online Academy!</h1>
                    <p>Are you enthusiastic about education and technology? Do you want to be a part of a team that is revolutionizing the way we learn? Then Alef Online Academy will be your launch pad!</p>
                    <button class="apply-button">Apply</button>
                </div>
                <div class="banner-image">
                    <img src="~/img/rafiki.png" alt="Join ALEF">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="interns">
            <img src="~/img/interns.jpg" alt="Interns">
            <p>As an intern at Alef, you will not just be another cog in the wheel. You will be an innovator, a designer of tomorrow’s education system. We provide a safe ground for creativity, cooperation, and perpetual development. Here your ideas matter, and there are no limits to what you can do. Find endless possibilities to learn, grow, and have a significant impact on the world around you. Together, we’ll build something phenomenal.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="growth">
            <p>ALEF Online Academy is your gateway to innovation! We provide a dynamic environment where creativity, collaboration, and continuous growth thrive. Your ideas will be cherished, and there are no limits to what you can accomplish. Here, you'll have the opportunity to gain invaluable experience, and make a real difference in the lives of learners worldwide. If you're ready to challenge the status quo and drive educational transformation, ALEF Online Academy is the place for you.</p>
            <img src="~/img/group.jpg" alt="Growth">
        </section>

        <section class="join">
            <h2>Ready to embark on this exciting journey? Explore our open positions and join the ALEF family!</h2>
            <button class="apply-button">Apply</button>
        </section>
    </main>

    <div class="call-to-action">
        <h3>READY TO EMBARK ON THIS EXCITING JOURNEY?</h3>
        <p>Explore Our Open Positions And Join The ALEF Family!</p>
        <a href="#">Explore Positions</a>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
